name: Magic Ball: The Mountain #002

#002 / 004

The pandemic is forcing us to stay at home. 
I have been at home for months without doing outdoor activities. 
I don't know how much I miss holidays and outdoor activities. 
Through this magic ball I try to see and remember the places I want to go.
